author: Warhammer
description:
War Despots demand the best, and that’s what’s in store in this video. Join Dan as he paints darkened metals and glowing weapons on this Helsmiths of Hashut miniature, based on the Forge Anathema colour scheme.

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Contrast:
Creed Camo 
Hexwraith Flame 

Base:
Canoptek Alloy
Iron Hands Steel
Iron Warriors
Mephiston Red
Phoenician Purple
Rakarth Flesh 

Layer:
Administratum Grey
Dawnstone
Skullcrusher Brass
Stormhost Silver

Shade:
Targor Rageshade

Technical:
Lahmian Medium 

Tools:
Small Base Brush STC
Small Layer Brush STC
Small Dry Brush STC
Medium Shade Brush STC
If you enjoyed this and want to learn more, our YouTube channel has an array of beginner-friendly videos to get you started.
